metadata.name: SELF-PORTRAIT-01
metadata.description:
A triumphant creator sits upon his stripy steed, among the flowers and ready to ride into the next adventure.  
Zuphioh is his name, and for the past year, he has been King of the Zebras...Slowly but surely covering the blockchain in his black & white friends, and his funny little Irish accent.

Thank you everyone for being apart of my journey, and for loving my zebras. It genuinely means the world to me, coming from a background of never being able to sell my work, to having a whole audience of people who love and support me, really genuinely does mean everything.

Minted on Self-Deployed Contract (ZUPHIOH) & Part of The Zebra Collection.

Buyer of this NFT is rewarded with a 1/1 corresponding avatar to match this piece
